mst-ghs
==============

This is a C++ implementation of GHS algorithm for finding minimum-weight spanning tree (MST) in distributed systems.
==============

How to build?
  Start terminal and go to the 'mst-ghs' directory
  Execute 'make' command in the terminal
  That's it!
   
How to run?
  Go to the 'mst-ghs' directory
  Execute 'make run' in the terminal
  
